" /></blockquote><br />\n&quot;近年有啲參考書，如《商務新字典》、《朗文中文新詞典》，將兩個字反寫做「甴曱」。但係明初古籍《篇海類編》早有記載：曱，音押；甴，音扎。「曱甴」同現今粵音gaat6 zaat6較為接近，反寫反而讀音相去甚遠。 &quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16633979/art/20170110/19891483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16633979%2Fart%2F20170110%2F19891483&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1442de9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16633979%2Fart%2F20170110%2F19891483&h=d16e7fb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16633979/art/20170110/19891483</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF-%E7%94%B4%E6%9B%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E7%2594%25B4%25E6%259B%25B1%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7e89570a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E7%2594%25B4%25E6%259B%25B1%2F&h=94f29b8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF-%E7%94%B4%E6%9B%B1/</a> (陳凱文注意) <br />\n呢啲嘢唔好亂教, 有爭議就有爭議, 未有定論就未有定論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb83e0bf770332b1711da1c0b3115956ebe46c25","tid":245424,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正寫係甴曱 留意返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲嘢自己睇真啲先 say sorry"}]}